  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><u>Spa</u></strong></p>
<p>The impressive pools of the Adler Termae’s five-star spa uss natural waters that are heated to 36 degrees and look out over the stunning Tuscan countryside. It truly is a remarkable spot to sit back and relax. For even more pampering, there are a wide choice of treatments available from over 40 highly-trained doctors, beauticians and therapists.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Activities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free use of e-bikes and mountain bikes</li>
<li>Guided walks, bike tours and excursions</li>
<li>AKI Kids’ club for ages 4 and over, including daily supervised activities</li>
<li>Daily program of yoga, aqua gym and pilates</li>
<li>Visit the wine cellars (organised locally)</li>
<li>Large fitness room</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span>Free WiFi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
