  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This is the perfect hotel for a luxury Tuscan break. We can't get enough of the spa here with over 1,000 square meters of pools and some of the best views in Tuscany. There's so much to do here from the free bike and walking excursions to rejuvenating well-being programmes (payable locally). The food is excellent too - expect gourmet Tuscan dishes and locally-made wines. You can take a trip to the hotel's winery to see how they're made too.</p>]]></listingDescription>
